section#hero.is-selected
    .hero-wrap
    
        .hero--lead
            h1.lead--text
                | Front-end #[span.highlight developer], #[br] 
                | A touch of #[span.highlight analytics] #[br] 
                | With a twist of #[span.highlight lemon]

            figure.lead--images
                img(src= imgPath + 'javascript.gif', alt="")
                img(src= imgPath + 'kurt-lemon.gif', alt="")

        .hero--resume
            p From a business student to a programmer professional. #[br]Nowadays, I work as front-end developer at a startup and seeking to deepen knowledge in javascript, vanilla or frameworks such as Vue, React, Angular and D3.

            p Check here what I had been doing!
            
            p.hero--resume__links Download my #[a(href="#", target="_blank") curriculum] or check my #[a(href="#projects", class="what-trigger") projects] and #[a(href="#contacts", class="where-trigger") contacts].
        
